597
00:35:26,497 --> 00:35:28,038
I'll come with you to
the hospital tomorrow.

598
00:35:28,738 --> 00:35:30,467
What hospital?

599
00:35:30,468 --> 00:35:32,066
Well...

600
00:35:32,067 --> 00:35:34,437
