607
00:36:03,937 --> 00:36:05,067
Gosh.

608
00:36:06,207 --> 00:36:07,308
Gosh.

609
00:36:12,948 --> 00:36:15,517
Gosh. That feels so good.

610
00:36:17,247 --> 00:36:18,848
Anna, you should try it as well.

611
00:36:19,218 --> 00:36:21,987
