612
00:36:21,988 --> 00:36:23,016
How?

613
00:36:23,017 --> 00:36:26,956
I'm healed when I see my
granddaughter woo ri.

614
00:36:26,957 --> 00:36:28,828
I have no pain.

615
00:36:28,957 --> 00:36:31,427
