616
00:36:31,428 --> 00:36:33,598
I'd be full without eating.

617
00:36:34,267 --> 00:36:37,267
Veronica, you should
take care of yourself.

618
00:36:37,408 --> 00:36:39,037
You had pain all over your body...

619
00:36:39,038 --> 00:36:41,078
