divorced last year.

620
00:36:42,308 --> 00:36:45,046
Our Maria hasn't even gone on a trip...

621
00:36:45,047 --> 00:36:47,717
Being abstinent.

622
00:36:47,718 --> 00:36:48,747
Anna.

623
00:36:50,817 --> 00:36:52,517
- Anna.
- Yes?

624
00:36:52,848 --> 00:36:55,618
- Maria...
- What about woo ri?

625
00:36:56,597 --> 00:36:58,067
She's pregnant.

626
00:37:00,685 --> 00:37:03,755
Lee Kang jae, you jerk.

627
00:37:06,424 --> 00:37:07,763
Gosh.

628
00:37:07,764 --> 00:37:09,025
You jerk!

629
00:37:09,094 --> 00:37:11,133
How dare you do this
to my granddaughter?

630
00:37:11,134 --> 00:37:13,493
- Grandma, what are you doing?
- You good for nothing jerk.

631
00:37:13,494 --> 00:37:16,204
- Grandma.
- How dare you touch her?

632
00:37:16,205 --> 00:37:18,473
- What?
- What did I do?

633
00:37:18,474 --> 00:37:21,474
It's all over the church
that woo ri is pregnant.

634
00:37:22,145 --> 00:37:23,844
- What?
- Pregnant?

635
00:37:24,244 --> 00:37:26,743
You promised. How could you?

636
00:37:26,744 --> 00:37:30,485
- Grandma. It's not Kang jae.
- What?

637
00:37:30,585 --> 00:37:32,314
What do you mean?

638
00:37:32,315 --> 00:37:36,024
I am pregnant, but it's not Kang jae.

639
00:37:36,025 --> 00:37:37,094
What?

640
00:37:38,324 --> 00:37:40,295
Then, who?

641
00:37:45,335 --> 00:37:46,735
What's all this?

642
00:37:46,965 --> 00:37:50,304
How could this happen to a girl
who has been kind all her life?

643
00:37:51,174 --> 00:37:53,474
Say something.

644
00:37:59,614 --> 00:38:00,884
Anna.

645
00:38:01,614 --> 00:38:03,755
I heard the story,

646
00:38:04,815 --> 00:38:06,783
but it's out of the ordinary.

647
00:38:06,784 --> 00:38:08,525
Should we keep the child
since it's new life?

648
00:38:09,284 --> 00:38:12,624
Or have my granddaughter have an
abortion and make her a sinner?

649
00:38:12,625 --> 00:38:14,565
What should I do?

650
00:38:15,224 --> 00:38:17,965
Is this why I've been
to church all my life?

651
00:38:18,034 --> 00:38:20,364
To have my granddaughter
go through such a thing?

652
00:38:20,735 --> 00:38:23,065
What do I do with woo ri?

653
00:38:23,304 --> 00:38:27,244
I feel sorry for my woo ri.

654
00:38:29,505 --> 00:38:30,545
Anna.

655
00:38:50,665 --> 00:38:51,895
Have some tea.

656
00:38:52,965 --> 00:38:54,005
Yes.

657
00:38:54,965 --> 00:38:56,064
But...

658
00:38:56,065 --> 00:38:59,304
I know it's rude coming
to you so suddenly,

659
00:38:59,835 --> 00:39:01,404
but it's such an urgent matter.

660
00:39:02,744 --> 00:39:04,915
Please have my grandchild.

661
00:39:05,844 --> 00:39:07,314
- Excuse me?
- My son is the only child...

662
00:39:07,315 --> 00:39:08,884
But he can no longer make babies.

663
00:39:11,685 --> 00:39:13,384
I can't believe my son has no sperm.

664
00:39:14,324 --> 00:39:15,824
He's the eldest son.

665
00:39:15,924 --> 00:39:17,855
It's up to you...

666
00:39:18,154 --> 00:39:19,494
Whether my family lives on.

667
00:39:20,324 --> 00:39:21,895
