668
00:39:22,795 --> 00:39:23,964
Shall I kneel?

669
00:39:23,965 --> 00:39:26,895
No, this is not that kind of matter.

670
00:39:28,264 --> 00:39:31,774
I understand your
unfortunate circumstance.

671
00:39:31,775 --> 00:39:34,074
But as I told you before, I
have my circumstances as well.

672
00:39:37,415 --> 00:39:38,974
No need for a longer conversation.
Get rid of this.

673
00:39:39,545 --> 00:39:42,114
- Yes?
- Get rid of the fruit basket.

674
00:39:42,915 --> 00:39:43,915
Right.

675
00:40:01,764 --> 00:40:03,034
You should take this.

676
00:40:04,705 --> 00:40:06,605
We have enough apples
as well, thank you.

677
00:40:08,705 --> 00:40:10,444
It was difficult in such
situations back in the day.

678
00:40:10,775 --> 00:40:12,645
There weren't any 50-dollar bills.

679
00:40:13,315 --> 00:40:15,315
Stuffing the box with
ten-dollar bills...

680
00:40:15,645 --> 00:40:16,784
Barely came up to 200,000 dollars.

681
00:40:17,315 --> 00:40:18,585
It became more convenient now.

682
00:40:19,215 --> 00:40:21,854
I filled up this box with
one million dollars...

683
00:40:21,855 --> 00:40:23,025
For you to take.

684
00:40:23,485 --> 00:40:25,223
- Excuse me?
- I, Kim duk bae,

685
00:40:25,224 --> 00:40:27,724
do not behave that
indecently in my old age.

686
00:40:28,125 --> 00:40:30,224
I'm not trying to ruin your life.

687
00:40:30,594 --> 00:40:32,263
We are in a difficult situation...

688
00:40:32,264 --> 00:40:34,104
And ask for a difficult favour.

689
00:40:34,105 --> 00:40:35,364
If you would just have the child,

690
00:40:36,404 --> 00:40:38,804
we will make the right
compensation for it.

691
00:40:40,105 --> 00:40:42,375
I'm sorry, Ms. woo ri.

692
00:40:42,574 --> 00:40:45,215
I kept on telling you our
side of the story...

693
00:40:45,474 --> 00:40:49,145
And left out what we would do for you.

694
00:40:50,985 --> 00:40:53,485
Stay abroad for about ten months.

695
00:40:53,585 --> 00:40:57,924
Think of it as going
to a language school.

696
00:40:58,094 --> 00:41:00,593
I'll give you a million now and
a million more after the baby.

697
00:41:00,594 --> 00:41:02,125
I'll give you two million in total.

698
00:41:08,835 --> 00:41:10,205
Two million dollars...

699
00:41:11,423 --> 00:41:12,583
If that's not enough,

700
00:41:12,784 --> 00:41:14,253
just tell me how much you want.

701
00:41:14,654 --> 00:41:16,493
I'll give you as much as you want.

702
00:41:16,494 --> 00:41:18,594
Just have our child, that's all.

703
00:41:21,793 --> 00:41:23,332
