and turn her life around!

705
00:41:26,634 --> 00:41:29,573
Two million dollars in ten months.
Then I'm set for life.

706
00:41:29,574 --> 00:41:30,873
I'd be totally up for that.

707
00:41:31,943 --> 00:41:33,203
It's a private loan.

708
00:41:33,204 --> 00:41:34,574
If you don't pay back,

709
00:41:34,914 --> 00:41:37,283
the interest becomes
larger than the principal.

710
00:41:37,284 --> 00:41:39,442
With 50,000 dollars,

711
00:41:39,443 --> 00:41:41,614
I'm confident I can make an
album and become a big hit.

712
00:41:53,293 --> 00:41:54,534
You don't want any apples?

713
00:41:56,463 --> 00:41:57,804
At least take the fruit basket.

714
00:42:05,904 --> 00:42:07,273
Father, what do we do?

715
00:42:07,643 --> 00:42:09,244
If she turns down money...

716
00:42:09,443 --> 00:42:10,614
That's how they are at first.

717
00:42:11,583 --> 00:42:13,914
