accepting money right away.

718
00:42:18,583 --> 00:42:20,123
Money solves everything.

719
00:42:29,233 --> 00:42:30,364
Goodness.

720
00:42:31,204 --> 00:42:33,063
What should we do, woo ri?

721
00:42:33,233 --> 00:42:34,403
What else is there to talk about?

722
00:42:34,404 --> 00:42:35,804
She'll get an abortion
tomorrow at the hospital.

723
00:42:36,804 --> 00:42:38,602
