carry out the pregnancy?

731
00:42:54,123 --> 00:42:56,154
Will the lord give her an award?
Will the government give her money?

732
00:42:57,193 --> 00:42:58,864
It's not a sin. She has
the right to do so.

733
00:42:59,923 --> 00:43:01,333
Woo ri's life can't be ruined.

734
00:43:01,434 --> 00:43:02,563
Mom. What about you?

735
00:43:03,634 --> 00:43:05,134
Did I ruin your life?

736
00:43:06,864 --> 00:43:07,872
What?

737
00:43:07,873 --> 00:43:09,333
I won't have the baby, so don't worry.

738
00:43:10,304 --> 00:43:12,003
